<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>I tested Zend_Http_Client incubator version working with Zend_Service_Amazon.</p>

<p>Zend_Service_Amazon has $_httpClient property it owns a Zend_Http_Client object.
And the object is created by following code in Zend_Service_Abstract at line 69.</p>

<pre><code>        self::$_httpClient = new Zend_Http_Client();
</code></pre>

<p>But Zend_Http_Client incubator version's cunstructor wants a required $uri parameter,
and it's the cause of fatal error.</p>

<p>If Zend_Http_Client incubator version replaces to the current version, it will be fixed.</p>

